I noticed something interesting: `SharedPreferencesPlugin.onAttachedToEngine(...)` is not called when I run into that bug.

My workaround is currently to invoke that method in my `MainActivity` myself. My `MainActivity.kt` looks now more or less like this:
```kotlin
class MainActivity : FlutterFragmentActivity() {
  override fun configureFlutterEngine(flutterEngine: FlutterEngine) {
    GeneratedPluginRegistrant.registerWith(flutterEngine)
  }
} 
```

